Interface QueryParser<QB extends QueryBuilder<QB>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoolQueryParser, BoostingQueryParser, CommonTermsQueryParser, ConstantScoreQueryParser, DisMaxQueryParser, ExistsQueryParser, FieldMaskingSpanQueryParser, FunctionScoreQueryParser, FuzzyQueryParser, GeoBoundingBoxQueryParser, GeoDistanceQueryParser, GeoDistanceRangeQueryParser, GeohashCellQuery.Parser, GeoPolygonQueryParser, GeoShapeQueryParser, HasChildQueryParser, HasParentQueryParser, IdsQueryParser, IndicesQueryParser, MatchAllQueryParser, MatchNoneQueryParser, MatchQueryParser, MissingQueryParser, MoreLikeThisQueryParser, MultiMatchQueryParser, NestedQueryParser, PrefixQueryParser, QueryStringQueryParser, RangeQueryParser, RegexpQueryParser, ScriptQueryParser, SimpleQueryStringParser, SpanContainingQueryParser, SpanFirstQueryParser, SpanMultiTermQueryParser, SpanNearQueryParser, SpanNotQueryParser, SpanOrQueryParser, SpanTermQueryParser, SpanWithinQueryParser, TemplateQueryParser, TermQueryParser, TermsQueryParser, TypeQueryParser, WildcardQueryParser, WrapperQueryParser

    public interface QueryParser<QB extends QueryBuilder<QB>>
    Defines a query parser that is able to read and parse a query object in XContent format and create an internal object representing the query, implementing QueryBuilder, which can be streamed to other nodes.
